title: Copycat(1995)(Sigourney Weaver)
description:
Description:
Criminal profiler and psychologist Dr Helen Hudson becomes entangled in the deadly mind game of a
vicious copycat serial killer Peter Foley. Due to the horrific attack Helen suffered in her past
as an agoraphobic she is confined to her apartment. The killer uses this against her in his
murderous attempts to become a famous serial killer. Detectives M. J Monahan and Reuben Goetz
they have the challenge of trying to capture the killer before he kills again and uses his
chance to commit another atrocious murder.
